    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Usage</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[15px] text-muted-foreground">Uses the native Popover API for open/close, click outside to dismiss, and Escape key. JS adds positioning, focus management, and arrow key navigation for <code>.popover-menu</code>.</p>
    <div class="snippet mt-4" data-active style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
